description: Matt Chapman’s two-run single highlighted a three-run eighth inning and six San Francisco pitchers combined for a four-hitter as the Giants beat the Chicago Cubs 5-1.
title: Matt Chapman drives in 2 runs and 6 Giants pitchers limit Cubs to four hits in a 5-1 win

description: Many states are failing to track how frequently children in foster care facilities are abused, sexually assaulted or improperly restrained, leaving them vulnerable to mistreatment.
title: States fail to track abuses in foster care facilities housing thousands of children, US says

title: Baby cousin with cancer inspires girls to sew hospital gowns for sick kids across U.S. and Africa

description: A new poll finds that most U.S. adults plan to watch or listen to some element of Thursday's presidential debate.
title: Most Americans plan to watch Biden-Trump debate: AP-NORC Poll

description: Ketel Marte hit a two-run homer in the first inning and drove in the go-ahead run with an infield hit in the seventh as the Arizona Diamondbacks beat the Minnesota Twins 5-4.
title: Marte knocks in go-ahead run in 7th and Diamondbacks edge Twins 5-4

description: A man accused of killing seven people and injuring dozens more at a Fourth of July parade in suburban Chicago in 2022 is expected to change his initial plea of not guilty.
title: Illinois man accused in mass shooting at Fourth of July parade expected to change not-guilty plea

title: Biden and Trump are set to debate. Here's what their past performances looked like
